TY  - JOUR
TI  - Towards an Economic Theory of Replacement Investment
AU  - Feldstein, Martin S.
AU  - Rothschild, Michael
AB  - [This paper develops an economic theory of replacement investment that can provide a basis for specifying an econometric model of investment behavior. The long-run and short-run effects of changes in the interest rate and in tax laws are examined. The paper also investigates several reasons why the common assumption of a technologically constant rate of replacement is incorrect even as an asymptotic limit.]
