TY  - JOUR
TI  - An Axiomatic Characterization of the Price Mechanism
AU  - Sonnenschein, Hugo
AB  - [A set of independent axioms are exhibited which characterize the price mechanism. The Debreu-Scarf limit theorem on the core of an economy and a category theory viewpoint are employed in the analysis.]
